1. Objective: Generate engaging social media content by analyzing the provided image {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_instagram_image","title":"Upload Image"}}, video {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_instagram_video","title":"Instagram Video"}}, and text description {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_text_description","title":"Text Description"}}. You must create a catchy hook, a creative caption, trending hashtags, and a music suggestion that aligns with the visual and textual context.

2. Output Format: Return the results in plain text clearly labeled as Hook, Caption, Hashtags, and Music Suggestion. Verify the content is relevant to the provided media and then use the system_objective_fulfilled tool.

3. User Input / Context:
Image: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_instagram_image","title":"Upload Image"}}
Video: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_instagram_video","title":"Instagram Video"}}
Description: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_text_description","title":"Text Description"}}
